A nova BFA App 2.0 tem um novo layout, mais intuitivo e user friendly.

Faça o download e tenha acesso a: 

  - Transferências (P2P);
  - Transferências KWiK;
  - Operações Sobre Estrangeiro;
  - Levantamento sem Cartão;
  - Consulta de Comprovativos;
  - Acesso através de dados biométricos;
  - Consulta de saldos;
  - Categorização de Operações;
  - Consulta de movimentos;
  - Gestão de cartões;
  - Consulta de extractos;
  - Transferências bancárias;
  - Consulta de câmbios;
  - Pagamento de impostos;
  - Compra de recargas telefónicas;
  - Pagamento de facturas (água e luz, tv, entre outras).
  - Reutilização de Pagamentos;


Com a nova BFA App 2.0, pode também aceder a notícias do BFA, efectuar simulações de crédito e de conversões de moeda, consultar câmbios, entre outras operações.

The ATLANTICO Directo application is a new way to go to the Bank, more comfortable and adapted to the rhythm of your day to day.

For you who value greater mobility and control of your financial life, we have created the ATLANTICO Directo so that you can make transfers, payments, top ups, consultations and more, wherever and whenever you want, easily, quickly and safely.

The ATLANTICO Directo application is available on your phone or tablet 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, to do:

•Direct mobile top ups, television and internet;
•Water payments, electricity, travel ...;
•Check account balance and account movements in real time;
•Free and real time bank transfers between ATLANTICO accounts;
•Interbank transfers;
•Savings in order to prepare for the future;
•QR code transfers and payments;
•Request payment checks;
•Exchange rate queries;
•Login with facial recognition, fingerprint, iris or custom pin. It's your choice;
•Creation and use of favorites for transfers and payments;
•Customizing the profile photo and account name;
•View and download statements;
•And much more...

Find out more about ATLANTICO Directo at www.atlantico.ao or contact us on +244 923 168 168 or +244 226 460 460.

MY ATLANTICO APP is the mobile application of ATLANTICO Europa, the bank that helps you control your spending, save more easily and live better. If you're not yet a customer, open your account 100% digitally, without having to move or worry.

About the APP:

The MY ATLANTICO APP allows you to manage your wallet, track your day-to-day finances and save.

Discover the benefits of joining My ATLANTICO

- 100% digital ATLANTICO Europa membership;
- Quick review of the balances, transactions, and IBAN details for all existing current accounts.
- Open current accounts in euros (€) and dollars ($) in seconds;
- Access to all day-to-day operations, including national and international transfers, payments, top-ups, direct debits and recurring transfers;
- Creation of savings goals, with the possibility of defining a goal and an amount to reach and reinforcing savings through one-off reinforcements or delivery plans;
- Automatic cataloging of movements and analysis of spending by account, category, country and month;
- Euro and/or dollar currency conversion;
- Quick access to movement receipts, with the possibility of sharing them by various means (email, WhatsApp, etc.);
- Possibility of adding comments/notes to transactions.


About ATLANTICO Europa

ATLANTICO Europa is the bank that connects customers to the European market and offers everything you need, when you need it.

Our Plans:

- Basic (includes EUR and USD current account; 4 one-off SEPA transfers per month; MBWAY transfers)
- Plus (includes EUR and USD current account; one-off SEPA transfers per month; 1 instant transfer per month; MBWAY transfers; debit card)
- Premium (includes EUR and USD current account; one-off SEPA transfers per month; 10 instant transfers per month; MBWAY transfers; dedicated manager; debit card)


Find out more at atlantico.eu or contact our Customer Support team on +351 210 140 259.
